---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Foto from "public/chris.png";
---

<Layout title="Landing - Christian Lara">
  <div class="landing">
    <section
    class="relative flex flex-col-reverse items-center justify-center w-full min-h-screen px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-20 mx-auto md:flex-row gap-8 md:gap-12"
    id="hero"
  >
    <!-- Texto -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-6/12 space-y-6 text-left">
      <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-light leading-tight py-2 sm:py-3">
          <span class="text-white block">¡Holaa! soy</span>
          <span class="font-extrabold mt-2 block">Christian Gael Lara Martínez</span>
        </h2>
  
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight text-white">
          Estudiante en <br />
          <span class="text-white font-extrabold font-outline-sm md:font-outline">
            Ingeniería en Computación
          </span>
        </h2>
  
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold">
          <span class="font-bold text-white">Soy</span>
          <span id="changing-word" class="highlight">Versatil</span>
        </h2>
  
        <p class="text-white text-sm sm:text-base font-light leading-relaxed tracking-wide">
          Soy una persona apasionada y creativa, con un enfoque innovador y versátil.
          Mi experiencia combina habilidades técnicas sólidas con una perspectiva humana, lo que me permite diseñar soluciones que no solo son eficientes, sino también significativas para las personas.
          <br /><br />
          Disfruto explorar nuevas ideas, desarrollar proyectos que integren tecnología con creatividad, y colaborar en equipo para materializar visiones en proyectos funcionales y accesibles.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Social media icons -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/christian-gael-lara-martinez-1252251bb/"
          class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex justify-center items-center border-2 border-white rounded-full shadow-md hover:scale-110 transition">
          <i class='bx bxl-linkedin text-xl sm:text-2xl'></i>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/ChristianLaraa"
          class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex justify-center items-center border-2 border-white rounded-full shadow-md hover:scale-110 transition">
          <i class='bx bxl-github text-xl sm:text-2xl'></i>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:christianlara225@aragon.unam.mx"
          class="w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex justify-center items-center border-2 border-white rounded-full shadow-md hover:scale-110 transition">
          <i class='bx bx-envelope text-xl sm:text-2xl'></i>
        </a>
        <a href="public/CV_ChristianLara.pdf"
          class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 sm:px-4 sm:py-2 border-2 border-white rounded-full shadow-md hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
          <i class='bx bx-file text-xl sm:text-2xl'></i>
          <span class="text-white text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold">Descargar CV</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <!-- Imagen -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-6/12 flex justify-center md:justify-end -mt-4 sm:-mt-6 md:mt-0">
      <img
        src="/chris.png"
        alt="Foto de Christian Lara"
        class="w-[70%] max-w-[320px] sm:max-w-[360px] md:w-[420px] md:h-[420px] rounded-full shadow-2xl object-cover"
      />
    </div>
  </section>
  
  </div>

  <style>
.landing {
  background: #0032A0;
  color: #EDFF44;
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
}

.font-outline-sm {
  -webkit-text-stroke: 1.2px white;
  color: transparent;
}

@media (min-width: 768px) {
  .font-outline {
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px white;
    color: transparent;
  }
}

.highlight {
  color: #EDFF44;
  font-weight: bold;
  position: relative;
}

.word-fade {
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 0.5s ease-in-out;
}

.word-fade.active {
  opacity: 1;
}

  </style>

  <script>
    const words = ["Creativo", "Analítico", "Desarrollador", "Artista", "Colaborador"];
    const wordElement = document.getElementById("changing-word");
    let index = 0;

    function changeWord() {
      wordElement.classList.remove("active");
      setTimeout(() => {
        index = (index + 1) % words.length;
        wordElement.textContent = words[index];
        wordElement.classList.add("active");
      }, 500);
    }

    setInterval(changeWord, 2500); // cada 2.5 segundos
    wordElement.classList.add("active"); // iniciar con fade-in
  </script>

</Layout>
